filters
Class Filter

java.lang.Object
  filters.Filter
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseFractionFilter, BlastFilter, EnzymeFilter, FailScoreFilter, GCFilter, LowerCaseFilter, NCountFilter, TMFilter
public abstract class Filter
extends java.lang.Object

The base class for all Filters. Forces subclasses to implement a method that filters an ArrayLit of Oligos in a certain way, a method that returns the oligos that have been rejected by the specific subclass, and a method that returns the specific type of filter that the subclass is
